Class JavaFXComponents

java.lang.Object
com.example.pizasson.utils.JavaFXComponents
public class JavaFXComponents extends Object
This class will be used as an util to implement the methods in the controller required. The methods provided from this class returns JavaFX Components created with different parameters.
